@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    ViewData["Breadcrumb"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="max-w-lg">
    <div class="mb-4">
        <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">Last updated: February 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-sm" style="color: var(--muted-fg); line-height: 1.7;">
        <h6 class="fw-semibold mt-3 mb-1" style="color: var(--fg);">1. Information We Collect</h6>
        <p>We collect personal information during registration including your name, email, NRIC, date of birth, and resume. Sensitive data such as NRIC is encrypted before storage.</p>

        <h6 class="fw-semibold mt-3 mb-1" style="color: var(--fg);">2. How We Use Your Information</h6>
        <p>Your information is used to manage your membership account and ensure account security through two-factor authentication and activity logging.</p>

        <h6 class="fw-semibold mt-3 mb-1" style="color: var(--fg);">3. Data Security</h6>
        <p>We implement industry-standard security including encryption, secure password hashing, session management, and audit logging.</p>

        <h6 class="fw-semibold mt-3 mb-1" style="color: var(--fg);">4. Contact</h6>
        <p class="mb-0">Questions? Email <a href="mailto:privacy@acejobagency.com" class="link">privacy@acejobagency.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
</div>
